Bankruptcies, Fraud & Unpaid Bills! Dance Moms Biggest Financial Scandals Revealed
Radar Staff, provided by
Published 3:04am, Tuesday, May 3, 2016
Photo: AMI Editors
Image 1of/10
CaptionClose
Image 1 of 10
Although the stars of Dance Moms are bringing in thousands from the hit show, theyre not safe from financial scandals! From Abby Lee Millers fraud charge to Melissa Zieglers bankruptcy, check out all of the times the cast members had money troubles. less
