Photo: AMI Editors
Image 2 of 10
Maddie Zieglers parents filed for chapter 7 bankruptcy in May of 2009. Kurt and Melissa, who were married at the time of the joint filing, owed $1,214,284.15 to creditors. Some debts included $908,000 in mortgages for three properties, $206,002 in credit card payments and more. The case was discharged in July of 2010. less
