Photo: Getty Images
Image 3 of 10
Newest cast member Ashley Allen, who was brought on the show so her daughter Brynn could be the next Maddie, filed for chapter 7 bankruptcy herself in January 2008. Ashlee and Aaron, who are now divorced, owed $1,405,903.80 to creditors. They racked up $1,131,668 in mortgage payments for two properties, $158, 334 in credit card payments and more. The case was discharged in April of 2008, with the family forced to surrender one of their homes and two cars. less
