Image 4 of 10
Dance teacher Abby Lee Miller was indicted on 20 counts of fraud in October 2015. She has been charged with concealment of bankruptcy assets, false bankruptcy declarations and bankruptcy fraud. Miller, 49, could face up to five years in prison and $5 million in fines if convicted. less
